{"tid":1449061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一間世界級嘅鐵路公司","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:08.000Z","uid":169266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6834930b37d664875428a0660db1894817fcf1","tid":1449061,"uid":169266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"今晚<br />\n係香港人都會好嬲<br />\n不過有更嬲嘅事係<br />\n犬隻係站內放彈，影響唔係一瞬間嘅事亦唔會只影響一個站嘅人；係成個網絡嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有做港鐵維修嘅朋友告知，毒煙一經進入地鐵冷氣系統可能入埋條行車隧道，列車行駛會把氣體帶去其他站，唔係一個站出事咁簡單。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家情況係好撚危險，麻煩大家幫手傳開去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ef0e87e7ca1b72280f7f86e88fdedfaa4b70f3","tid":1449061,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1C5doR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1C5doR0.jpg&h=f6222da1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3qg55m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3qg55m.jpg&h=284831ce&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}